race.comment: MY SWEETHEART (9) made progress last start to finish third over 1200m at Gilgandra after being in contention on the corner. Likely improver with strong prospects. NAMARA (10) settled back but wound up late to finish fourth when resuming last start over 1108m at Port Macquarie. Races well when second-up. Among the leading chances. SORUTAL (12) is a four-start maiden who resumed with a handy seventh over 1100m at Armidale. Bold showing expected with added fitness this time. MANAFTERMIDNIGHT (6) is a gelding by Capitalist on debut. Gets the inside draw and the stable has an impressive strike rate with the first-starters. Keep safe.
